{"tid":1702880,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"尚德公祭「你不會白犧牲」","createTime":"2019-11-10T03:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T03:52:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"67b3622e48a24a7f2ee3bf35936b09c37c4299ce","tid":1702880,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T03:35:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191110/PT6GDYUINZIQRIGUKJPUYGTM6M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191110%2FPT6GDYUINZIQRIGUKJPUYGTM6M%2F&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpnHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=7e337683\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191110%2FPT6GDYUINZIQRIGUKJPUYGTM6M%2F&h=0c00e3ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191110/PT6GDYUINZIQRIGUKJPUYGTM6M/</a><br />\n<br />\n尚德公祭「你不會白犧牲」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】22歲科大生周梓樂上周一凌晨在將軍澳尚德邨停車場墮樓重創，延至前日早上傷重不治，事發現場成為巿民悼念公祭地點，昨續有大批巿民獻花及留言表達心意，人流由早至晚絡繹不絕，有人到場後忍不住熱淚盈眶，又指如此多證據顯示警察濫權濫捕，政府仍然視若無睹，讓年輕生命悄然流逝；亦有人在停車場外自製小型祭壇及花壇，為周同學默哀。<br />\n<br />\n記者：梁瑞帆 江子堯<br />\n<br />\n周梓樂由三樓墮至二樓的停車場位置繼續成為其公祭靈堂，擺在欄河的鮮花擺滿四叠，猶如白色花海，柱及牆上滿佈便利貼、紙鶴及連豬，有人在紙寫上「周同學，願終有一日我們在自由的國度相見」、「願你安息，香港人一定幫你搵出真相，餘下的路我哋會代你行埋落去」，亦有人在天花板掛上一張白紙板，以將軍澳街坊署名寫上「你不會白犧牲的，全港正義市民誓要追究警暴。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/J3OLegD4voo4_CLVYB7PLCQ1KFo=/802x531/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/HBFQOYHFSGPRRV5O5SYGUNNQNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FJ3OLegD4voo4_CLVYB7PLCQ1KFo%3D%2F802x531%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FHBFQOYHFSGPRRV5O5SYGUNNQNY.jpg&h=093c452f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尚德邨停車場放滿白花，掛滿紙鶴，人流由早至晚絡繹不絕。謝榮耀攝<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/N7Nsa5fQPGJOQiny7lRz9am9AfU=/802x531/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/6BNWJMQKAASTGOVMXI2NGD4E7Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FN7Nsa5fQPGJOQiny7lRz9am9AfU%3D%2F802x531%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F6BNWJMQKAASTGOVMXI2NGD4E7Y.jpg&h=80160d9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n年輕生命悄然流逝，到場哀悼梓樂的市民不禁落淚。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/Y88kUoJyYFtprG8-H0cJlRbMkeE=/802x531/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/PUIFZ4HOFUJAADJ7MMO6SNZLTA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FY88kUoJyYFtprG8-H0cJlRbMkeE%3D%2F802x531%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FPUIFZ4HOFUJAADJ7MMO6SNZLTA.jpg&h=bcce56a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n停車場外設祭壇，市民以佛教儀式為梓樂誦經。梁瑞帆攝<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/dJYr5YSSbXeLhGXDYdcLl3wxrX8=/802x1198/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/SWL775KSHRVAAGBKBCX35EEHOA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FdJYr5YSSbXeLhGXDYdcLl3wxrX8%3D%2F802x1198%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FSWL775KSHRVAAGBKBCX35EEHOA.jpg&h=365bf3c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巿民在場留言表達心意，指要代梓樂走下去。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n悼念者：堅持到真相大白<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：性侵傳聞不絕 女生脫口罩控訴<br />\n<br />\n繼基督教徒前晚進行追思會後，再有佛教徒接力，昨早在停車場外設置小祭壇，法師敲木魚為梓樂誦經超度，善信跪地鞠躬拜祭，相隔數米，牆上擺上梓樂的黑白相，牆上貼上大字報「他只有22歲」，地上擺滿鮮花如花壇，有巿民跪地叩首，誦念祝禱。<br />\n<br />\n入夜後聚集巿民增加，職員用雪糕筒圍封附近停車泊位，以便容納更多人，牆邊多了白洋燭砌上不同形狀，有人砌上RIP或十字架圖案，全部人均沒有叫口號，哀悼後離開，間中出現啜泣聲，氣氛平靜。<br />\n<br />\n彭小姐專程前來獻花悼念，坦言「我覺得佢哋（警方）係咁掩飾真相！」途中忍不住落淚稱「我諗緊點解一個22歲年輕人，會發生咁嘅事，同一時間，我諗返自己22歲嘅時候做緊乜嘢，我覺得好唔開心，我覺得社會好唔公平，咁多證據顯示警察濫捕濫權，但我哋都做唔到啲乜嘢，因為政府唔肯聽我哋講嘢」，聲言會堅持等待真相大白。<br />\n<br />\n尚德邨對開街頭前晚多次爆發衝突，一夜過後回復平常，惟仍有大堆磚頭、滅火筒、單車堵塞天橋樓梯上，行人需要大步跨過，唐明街與唐俊街一組交通燈中午故障，途經車輛需要慢駛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/X99nhGRj5hyz2y63vIfU6WD-Qr8=/802x432/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/FWHYOBX3TVPCZP7XNOEUSMTU6M.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FX99nhGRj5hyz2y63vIfU6WD-Qr8%3D%2F802x432%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FFWHYOBX3TVPCZP7XNOEUSMTU6M.gif&h=6a6ce90b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAppleDaily"},{"pid":"c26da4cad2ba8cb665e143c0a5bfc8cac27407a0","tid":1702880,"uid":321684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T03:52:35.000Z","msg":"P牌想推但推唔郁<br />\n<br />\n美國陣線要人呀!!! 有冇識人呀??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1702811/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1702811/page/1</a>"}]}